      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. i catch myself starting to say something to him before i remember. then the silence just hits me all over again. i dont even know why i bother waking up just to sit in this emptiness. it feels like i'm just a ghost walking through rooms that don't belong to me anymore.",
