    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just noise though. it's like the whole purpose of my life went with him. everything i do feels so pointless, like i'm just going through the motions of a life that ended months ago. i look at the bed and i just think... what is even the point of being here if the person i was meant to be with isn't? it just feels so heavy and senseless.",
