      "content": "but \"deciding what comes next\" feels impossible because there is no \"next.\" there's just this hollow version of me. i look at everything around the house and i just feel like i'm waiting for something that's never going to happen. it honestly feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, useless weight around for no reason. like, why am i even forcing myself to keep holding on to a life that doesn't even feel real anymore?",
